                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 tracking-tighter leading-tight mb-6">Open Company in UK for Non-Residents | 2026 Guide</h1>
                    <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 font-medium leading-relaxed mb-6">You don't need to be a <strong>uk resident</strong> to launch your vision. We help founders from <strong>anywhere in the world</strong> to **open a company in the uk** and manage their **company details** with 100% transparency.</p>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-10">As authorized <strong>formation agents</strong>, we make it easy to **form a uk company** from start to finish. Our packages include a professional **registered office address**, assistance to **open a uk business bank account**, and guidance on how to **register for vat** and **register for corporation tax**.</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                        <a href="/pricing" class="btn-primary" aria-label="View Company Formation Packages">Start Company Formation</a>
                        <a href="/faq" class="px-10 py-5 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-50 transition shadow-sm" aria-label="Frequently Asked Questions">Read FAQs</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
