                    <p class="text-gray-500 font-medium leading-relaxed text-sm">Every **uk based** **limited company** is **legally required** to have an address in Britain. We provide a prestigious **registered office address** that satisfies **Companies House** while protecting your personal privacy.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 2 -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-10 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 text-brand-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">Directors and Shareholders</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 font-medium leading-relaxed text-sm">Non-residents can be 100% **directors and shareholders** of a UK firm. You do not need **uk resident directors** to qualify. We handle the identity verification and **person with significant control** (PSC) reporting for you.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Card 3 -->
                <div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-10 border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition">
                    <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-50 text-brand-blue rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
