                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">UK Business Banking</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 font-medium leading-relaxed text-sm">While some **high street banks** may reject foreign directors, we provide specialized support to help you **open a uk business bank account**. Complete your **uk business banking** safely with partners like Wise, Payoneer, and Tide.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
